<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Windsheim, Schweinfurt und Weißenburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet nach Zusammenkunft des Landfriedens zu Bamberg um Gesandte am Montag nach dem Weißen Sonntag nach Nürnberg, wie man es allen fränkischen Reichsstädten mitgeteilt hat.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_174" id="85v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_174_r2l19"><expan>Winſdh<ex>eim</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_174_r2l21"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_174_r2l20">
<del rend="strikethrough">ercʒelt </del></ab></add> <expan>vnſe<ex>r</ex></expan> frewnde / die yecʒund <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r2l22">dem <expan>Lantfr<ex>ide</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein </del> cʒü <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> vvie doſelbſt von etw </del> <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r2l23">ſein / ercʒelet / . vvie etlıch <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Stet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . doſelbſt cʒü <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r2l24">Jn geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ ſie güt dewcht / . daʒ wir ew vnd etlıch <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r2l25">Stete <expan>cʒeſam<ex>m</ex>en</expan> manten / daʒ man <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>etlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſachen redt vnd darvmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r2l26">cʒe rat würd 
<del rend="strikethrough">e </del> / des ein notdurft ſeÿ / . als die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vvol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r2l27"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / wenn ſie cʒü vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd alſo <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ewr frunde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r2l28">cʒü vns her gen <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> ſchıcken wollet / daʒ die auf den Montag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r2l29">nach <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Weiſſen Suntag cʒü Rat cʒeit beÿ vns ſein / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r2l30">deſgleichen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir / den <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan> Sweinfürt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r2l31"><expan>Weiſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_174_r2l32"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> Sweinfürt et <expan>vveiſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / <expan>ſi<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> / . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_174" id="85v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Winsdh<ex>eim</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan> frewnde, die yeczund
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> auf dem <expan>lantfr<ex>ide</ex></expan> czü
                                <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, erczelet, wie etlich
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>stet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> doselbst czü <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
                        mit in geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz sie güt dewcht, daz wir ew
                        und etlich <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> stete
                            <expan>czesam<ex>m</ex>en</expan> manten, daz man
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sachen redt und darumb cze rat würd, des
                        ein notdurft sey, als die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>neme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, wenn sie czü uns
                            <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und also <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir ewr frunde czü uns her gen <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> schicken
                        wollet, daz die auf den <app><note><q type="date">montag nach <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> weissen
                            suntag</q>25.02.1409</note></app> czü rat czeit bey uns sein; und desgleichen
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan>, Sweinfürt und
                            <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> auch
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> Sweinfürt et
                            <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
